Class BrowserPool

removeBrowser

public void removeBrowser(EmbeddedBrowser browser,
                          CrawlQueueManager terminationHandler)
Remove a browser from the pool, do not release it again as it might be faulty. A RuntimeException might be thrown when there are no more browsers left in the pool after removing this instance stopping all processing.

Parameters:
browser - the browser instance to be remove (not null)
terminationHandler - the call-back handler to call the terminate function on.
